This paper deals with distributed optimization, which is a common topic in machine learning and optimization, hence cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also deals with distributed computing and control, which suggests cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) as likely categories. The paper also deals with multi-agent systems, which suggests cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) as a likely category. Finally, the paper deals with information theory, which suggests cs.IT (Information Theory) as a possible category.
